Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.99,0:00:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.49,0:00:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The judgment has been\Nhanded down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.55,0:00:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.95,0:00:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Has this helped you understand the pain\N that other people feel, even a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.62,0:00:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even my arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.56,0:00:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Has his Jutsu done something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:00:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, that can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.75,0:01:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You have already fallen\Nunder my curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The ceremony will now begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.39,0:01:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not taste the ultimate pain\Nwith me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:58.36,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(670.313,595)}The Judgment\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You have already fallen\Nunder my curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.05,0:03:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The ceremony will now begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then! Why not taste\Nthe ultimate pain with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Captain Asuma burned?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't his opponent the one hit\Nby the Fire Style Jutsu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He definitely was hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But for some reason,\N Captain Asuma was also burned by the Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This...could it be that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This will net us 35 million in gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.25,0:03:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All the preparations are\Nnow complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.51,0:03:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to hurt like crazy,\Nso get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts, doesn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is nothing.\NI haven't got you in a vital spot yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe me,\NTHAT pain is out of this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The pain another feels while\Ndying penetrates into my own body!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.11,0:04:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I pass through the pain, transcend it,\Nand turn it into pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Asuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,is holding his left leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.26,0:05:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Something strange is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same injured leg as the opponent\N who stabbed himself with his own lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have already fallen\N{\i1}under my curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His body and mine are connected\N{\i1}with some curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In other words, the damage dealt\N{\i1}to our bodies is also linked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.59,0:05:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Furthermore, he is immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where would you like to hurt next?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Here? Or here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.77,0:06:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How about both legs\Nat the same time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.61,0:06:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,shall we end now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.12,0:06:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shikamaru! You must not use\Na physical attack like Shadow Sewing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop his movements with\NShadow Strangle Jutsu! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Better make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'd let that happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it, Shikamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:08:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't stop me for long!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumo, how many minutes have\N passed since you requested backup?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,About ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.32,0:08:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be at least another 20 minutes\Nbefore reinforcements arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...! What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If we kill him,\NCaptain Asuma will also die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, one must kill one's opponent\Nin order to break a long-lasting type Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But if that is not possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Every Jutsu inevitably has rules\N {\i1}associated with it, {\i1}as well as risks and pitfalls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.59,0:08:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}First, I need to calm down\N{\i1}and analyze the opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was saved,\N{\i1}thanks to Shikamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.85,0:08:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must take this chance and\N{\i1}think of a way to break this Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With him as an opponent,\N {\i1}the Shadow Strangle Jutsu{\i1} won't hold out that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's little time to consider\N{\i1}the next move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If this wears on any longer, I'll lend a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let all the money get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to butt out, Kakuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can handle this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.03,0:09:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Truth be told, the situation as it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}we're lucky the other guy has\N{\i1}stayed out of the fight for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be that as it may,\N{\i1}there's still the question of what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:10:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, it's all a matter of time now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.76,0:10:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it... Think back...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.24,0:10:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Surely, I've come this far assuming
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd be fighting against an adversary\N{\i1}beyond the scope of my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Akatsuki Organization\N{\i1}is made up of ten members.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Orochimaru withdrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasori of the Red Sand is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of the remaining ones,\N{\i1}we know the identities of three.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Kisame Hoshigaki, {\i1}who is reputed to\N have sparred {\i1}with Guy Sensei with ease...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He might be a Water Style User.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke's older brother,\N{\i1}Itachi Uchiha with his Sharingan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.83,0:11:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was his handiwork that put Kakashi\N{\i1}in the hospital for over a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Deidara, said to have sparred {\i1}with Naruto. \N{\i1}He uses animated explosive clay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.11,0:11:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He blew himself up in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's doubtful whether that story\N{\i1} is actually true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That leaves five members\N{\i1}of the Akatsuki Organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.55,0:11:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whichever of the faces\N{\i1}in this file you pick,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.18,0:11:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you'll find him to be one tough opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.19,0:11:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Their Ninjutsu will be of a level\N{\i1}that should not be underestimated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Though the true nature of\N{\i1}these five is unknown,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there is no doubt they have special abilities\N{\i1} that are beyond our imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're up against the worst possible\N{\i1} bunch of fellows.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When it comes to this, {\i1}it's meaningless\N to formulate {\i1}a strategy in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In fact, any preconceptions\N{\i1} might make matters worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.76,0:11:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It goes without saying that\N{\i1}we should train to get stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but what happens when you encounter{\i1}\N an adversary you can't defeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The nature and extent of\N{\i1}the enemy's powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}his Ninjutsu, Taijutsu, and Genjutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You must discern what type\N{\i1}of Ninja he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then you need to determine whether{\i1} or not it's a\N combined attack {\i1}by guys who function as a two-man cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.73,0:12:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And if there's a possibility of that, {\i1}then what kind\N of chemistry does {\i1}he have with his team members?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.15,0:12:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We need to gather as {\i1}much information as\N possible {\i1}and make a split second decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're up against an organization\Nlike the Akatsuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,there isn't even time to\Ngather such information, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.83,0:12:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Akatsuki, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.06,0:12:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you already taken action\Nagainst the Akatsuki Organization?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I came to the conclusion that\Nit was pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:13:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you got hold of even one piece of information about\N the enemy, it could lead to a successful strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If we could get our hands\Non such information.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's difficult since we're up\Nagainst the Akatsuki for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A guy like me would be blown away\Nin an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're probably right about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.13,0:13:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's mortifying,\Nbut those are guys who don't slack off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That is if you were to come up against\Nthe Akatsuki on a one-to-one basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You are one of the best at judging and analyzing\N a situation, even among the Hidden Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't find the time to strategize in a one-on-one combat,\N then depend upon your comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.63,0:13:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Team responsibility is important,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but one who does not rely upon his comrades...\N is not fulfilling that responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There are times when even if you can't do it alone,\N things will somehow work out
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.95,0:13:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,if you and your comrades\Npool each others strengths.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not enough for things to\Njust somehow work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.54,0:13:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Before your comrades get done in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Asuma has left me with\N{\i1}a wealth of information.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Think! You've got to think!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Remarks, personality, speech patterns...\N{\i1}the clothes they wear...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Grasp their movements\N{\i1}right up to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The significance of\N{\i1}each and every action.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then the connection between actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Develop a hypothesis about their abilities\N {\i1}that can be drawn from {\i1}all these factors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's all about observation and analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,God's judgment will be handed down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}God...judgment...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.43,0:14:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You have already fallen under my curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The ceremony will now begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A curse...the ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, all preparations are complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Preparations...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looks like Shikamaru\N{\i1}came up with an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.53,0:15:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you figure something out, Shikamaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.88,0:15:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's amazing that you're capable\N{\i1}of such an analysis
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}while still maintaining your Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shikamaru is endowed with\N{\i1}lightning powers of analysis
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that enable him to look ten steps ahead\N{\i1}and predict 200 more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's more, {\i1}he has the intuition to choose {\i1}the\N best possible strategy {\i1}based on that analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading out, Captain Asuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That Shadow Jutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:16:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does it force the person it's used on\N{\i1}to mirror the motions of its caster?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why you... Trying to sniff out the true nature\N{\i1} of my Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.27,0:16:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll draw that creep outside the strange\Npattern drawn on the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.63,0:16:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do that,\Nhis curse Jutsu will be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth does that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,His weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That huge scythe with three blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging by its shape, I'd say it's not\Ndesigned to land a single fatal blow,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but rather increase\Nhis attack range.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All his weapons are designed to\Ncause damage from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, his tactic is to\Nonly injure his opponent
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and then buy time to deploy\Na lethal Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And by that you mean the curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:17:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But what's the connection between\Nthe enemy's wound and the curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.13,0:17:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to form a link between himself\Nand his targeted opponent,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,he needs to find a way to incorporate\Nthat opponent's blood into his own body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So when he was licking the blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.83,0:17:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then if he wounds his opponent and\Neven a little blood adheres to that sickle...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,he can curse his opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.09,0:17:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,After licking the blood,\Nhis body changed color.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.38,0:17:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a condition for invoking the curse.\NBut that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to completely invoke the curse,\None more condition must be met.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,One more?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.63,0:17:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This brat knows his stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.49,0:17:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A little while ago, that creep let \NAsuma's Fire Style Jutsu roll right off him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He was unfazed, but he hurried back to that\N strange pattern drawn on the ground, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And once he was standing inside that pattern,\N he said the ceremony would begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.94,0:18:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And by howling that the preparations\Nwere now complete...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We can surmise the set-up\Nfor his art of cursing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is only complete once he steps\Ninside that pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.59,0:18:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.33,0:18:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You talk too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was able to figure\N{\i1}all that out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you! I'll get you later!\NI'll tear you limb from limb!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pulverize you! I'll turn you inside out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.89,0:18:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't going to be a "later"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We got him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! The curse is broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:18:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at my limit! I don't think\NI can hold him any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.84,0:19:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well, Shikamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakuzu! Lend me a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Snap to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to keep your wits\Nabout you.
